### ========================================================
### 代理商品配置 API 测试 (F-004)
### 服务: mall-admin / mall-toc-service / mall-agent-employee-service
### 生成时间: 2026-03-16
### ========================================================

### --------------------------------------------------------
### Admin 门面接口
### --------------------------------------------------------

### 查询代理商品列表
GET http://localhost:8080/admin/api/v1/agent-products?backendCategoryId=1001&agentStatus=1&pageNo=1&pageSize=10
X-User-Token: {{userToken}}

### 导入代理商品（xlsx文件上传）
POST http://localhost:8080/admin/api/v1/agent-products/import
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary
X-User-Token: {{userToken}}

------WebKitFormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="agent-products.xlsx"
Content-Type: application/vnd.openxmlformats-officedocument.spreadsheetml.sheet

[二进制文件内容]
------WebKitFormBoundary--

### 删除代理商品
DELETE http://localhost:8080/admin/api/v1/agent-products/SPU2024000004
X-User-Token: {{userToken}}

### --------------------------------------------------------
### App 门面接口
### --------------------------------------------------------

### 获取代理商品类目
GET http://localhost:8082/app/api/v1/agent-products/categories
Authorization: Bearer {{jwtToken}}

### 查询可代理商品列表
GET http://localhost:8082/app/api/v1/agent-products?categoryId=1001&pageNo=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{jwtToken}}

### --------------------------------------------------------
### Inner 内部服务接口
### --------------------------------------------------------

### 分页查询代理商品
POST http://localhost:8081/inner/api/v1/agent-products/page
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "backendCategoryId": 1001,
  "agentStatus": 1,
  "pageNo": 1,
  "pageSize": 10
}

### 批量导入代理商品
POST http://localhost:8081/inner/api/v1/agent-products/import
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "products": [
    {
      "spuCode": "SPU2024000006",
      "spuName": "测试商品6",
      "backendCategoryId": 1001,
      "backendCategoryName": "手机数码",
      "price": 5999.00
    }
  ],
  "operatorId": 10001
}

### 移除代理商品
POST http://localhost:8081/inner/api/v1/agent-products/remove
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "spuCode": "SPU2024000004",
  "operatorId": 10001
}

### 按后台类目查询商品
POST http://localhost:8081/inner/api/v1/agent-products/list-by-category
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "categoryId": 1001,
  "pageNo": 1,
  "pageSize": 10
}

### 检查SPU是否已代理
GET http://localhost:8081/inner/api/v1/agent-products/check-agented?spuCode=SPU2024000001

### 更新代理状态
POST http://localhost:8081/inner/api/v1/agent-products/update-status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "spuCode": "SPU2024000004",
  "agentStatus": 1,
  "operatorId": 10001
}

### 发布代理商品
POST http://localhost:8081/inner/api/v1/agent-products/release
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "spuCode": "SPU2024000004",
  "operatorId": 10001
}
